title: Nural - Entitlement 2009
description:
This is the 2009 album Entitlement by Nural.


I don't even know if these guys are active anymore, but i love this album.

I guess it would be classed as christian rock, but its not exactly preachy.


All in 192kps

Total duration 33:17


Track listing:


1. The Hits Keep Coming

2. Stop Me When You've Had Enough

3. Physics

4. Up Against

5. Say What You Will

6. Surefire

7. I've Been Here Before

8. Me or the Music

9. You've Got Some Nerve

10. Sweet Oblivion


Sorry its only in 192 but thats what i found it in, wherever i found it.

Anyway, its a great album.


Enjoy! :)
